60;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Perilla" title="Perilla">Perilla (<i>shiso</i>)</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Rosemary" title="Rosemary">Rosemary</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Common_Rue" title="Common Rue">Rue</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Common_sage" title="Common sage" class="mw-redirect">Sage</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Savory_(herb)" title="Savory (herb)" class="mw-redirect">Savory</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sorrel" title="Sorrel">Sorrel</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Tarragon" title="Tarragon">Tarragon</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Thyme" title="Thyme">Thyme</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Vietnamese_Coriander" title="Vietnamese Coriander" class="mw-redirect">Vietnamese coriander (<i>rau răm</i>)</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Woodruff" title="Woodruff">Woodruff</a></span></p>
